title: Bright Lincoln Square 1 Bedroom Heat Included Cats ok 9/1 $1025
posting_body: ['This bright and Sunny 1 Bedroom in vintage Lincoln Square walk up building has tons of light and a lots of windows.', '1st Floor unit.', ' Heat is included!', 'Cats Ok.', 'Hardwood floors throughout, tile in kitchen.', 'Dishwasher.', ' Laundry in building.', 'Great neighbors and park across the street.', 'Library down the block.', 'A 5 min walk to bars and restaurants down Lincoln Avenue.', '2 minute walk to Western brown line.', '  Super easy street parking.', "It doesn't get better than this for the price.", 'Will go fast!', 'Nice quiet building, great small management company.', ' Non smoking building.', 'Available September 1st.', 'Currently occupied.', '$25 application fee.', 'No credit check fee.', 'No move in fees.', 'NO DOGS!', 'NO PHONE CALLS PLEASE.', ' TEXT ONLY.', 'Requirements:', '1.', 'Full Security Deposit of $1025 prior to move in, no exceptions.', '(You get this back upon move out)', '2.', "First month's rent required before key exchange.", '3.', 'Minimum of 6 months of employment at current job with proof.', 'Showings available before 3pm Tuesday-Thursday & Sundays.', 'Friday-Monday more flexible.', '***EMAIL FOR MORE INFO OR TO SCHEDULE A SHOWING.', 'IF THIS LISTING IS STILL UP, THE UNIT IS STILL AVAILABLE.', '***']
